sources.title: Apocalypse Child (Full Movie) Drama, subtitled
sources.description:
A surfing instructor, raised to believe he is the illegitimate son of Francis Ford Coppola, finds himself in a love triangle as he looks for answers and reconnects with an old friend. Language Filipino and English (English Subtitles)

Directed by Mario Cornejo
2015
Starring Sid Lucero, Ana Abad Santos, RK Bagatsing
